UID:10009845-1775678400-1775683800@www.unexpectedproductions.org
SUMMARY:Duo Comedy Showcase 2026
DESCRIPTION:Seattle’s one and only open mic dedicated to two-person improv teams! Every week at Unexpected Productions\, two-person teams take the stage to create hilarious\, fast-paced\, totally unscripted comedy right before your eyes. No scripts\, no safety nets—just pure improv magic. \nAt Duos\, everyone shines. Newer performers sharpen their game. Seasoned improvisers experiment\, take risks\, and get wonderfully weird. The results? Quick-witted scenes\, surprising twists\, and bold choices that feel impossible until you watch them happen live. \nWhether you dream of being the next Key & Peele\, Tina Fey & Amy Poehler\, or a chaotic tag-team like Deadpool & Wolverine\, this is your chance to take the mic and run with it. All experience levels are welcome. Bring a friend\, form a team\, and give Seattle a show they won’t forget. To sign up your duo\, email duoshowcase@gmail.com. \nLooking for a midweek serotonin boost? Watching the show is just as fun as performing in it. Grab a seat\, grab a friend\, and discover why Unexpected Productions is the home of Seattle improv.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/duo-comedy-showcase-2026/2026-04-08/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/200-px-by-250-px-DUOs-.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260409T213000
DTSTAMP:20260407T194449
CREATED:20251204T005447Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251230T165100Z
UID:10010081-1775764800-1775770200@www.unexpectedproductions.org
SUMMARY:Loose Cannons 2026
DESCRIPTION:Loose Cannons is Seattle improv at its most unpredictable. Every performance at Unexpected Productions in Pike Place Market is a one-of-a-kind experience: exciting\, unexpected\, a little dangerous\, and always ridiculously fun. This is the show where anything can happen and usually does. \nPart One: Part One: The night kicks off with a unique performance\, setting the performers in a new format with special guest improvisers showcasing their signature style or a never-before-seen format. Your suggestions fuel the fire\, and the improvisers will ignite the stage\, bringing your ideas to life. \nPart Two: The second half launches from a single audience suggestion\, setting the performers in motion. It might start with a song\, a monologue\, or a rapid-fire group connection game. Whatever emerges will inspire spontaneous stories\, surprising twists\, and big comedic swings. \nLoose Cannons is fueled by audience ideas\, fearless performers\, and the thrill of not knowing what happens next. You light the fuse. They run with it. What they create is entirely up to you.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/loose-cannons-2026/2026-04-09/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/cannon_px-lrg-250x200-1-2.jpg
END:VEVENT
