LAST-MODIFIED:20260126T180334Z
UID:10011232-1775849400-1775853900@www.unexpectedproductions.org
SUMMARY:Seattle Suites: An Improvised Neil Simon Comedy
DESCRIPTION:Improvised comedy in the style of Neil Simon\, where one hotel suite becomes a comedic pressure cooker for 3 hilarious improvised tales\n\n\n\nOne hotel suite. Countless misunderstandings. Relentless laughs. \nSeattle Suite is a laugh-driven\, fully improvised play inspired by the style of Plaza Suite and California Suite\, capturing the signature humor of Neil Simon that is fast\, verbal\, and rooted in beautifully human flaws. Each night\, a single Seattle hotel room becomes the setting for interconnected scenes inspired by your suggestions\, friends overshare and spiral\, romantic gestures go wrong\, awkward silences stretch\, and small problems become big ones. The comedy comes from character and relationship\, building through sharp dialogue\, escalating tension\, and recognizable\, lived-in situations. Perfect for fans of smart comedy\, relationship humor\, and classic theatrical wit.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-suites-an-improvised-neil-simon-comedy/2026-04-10/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Seattle-Suite_-Comedy-in-the-Clouds.png
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T213000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260410T230000
DTSTAMP:20260407T194449
CREATED:20260123T174220Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260123T174348Z
UID:10011103-1775856600-1775862000@www.unexpectedproductions.org
SUMMARY:Seattle Theatresports 2026
DESCRIPTION:Seattle’s high-energy improv battle where your suggestions shape every scene. Fast\, funny\, unpredictable comedy Fri. & Sat. 9:30\n\n\n\nWelcome to Seattle’s funnest improv comedy show\, a high-energy\, no-rules showdown where your ideas shape every scene. Seattle Theatresports at Unexpected Productions’ Market Theater in Pike Place Market is part comedy battle\, part game night\, and completely powered by the crowd. Boo the judges. Cheer the Gum Wall race and laugh til it hurts! \nEvery show\, two teams of top Seattle improvisers go head to head\, performing games\, stories\, characters\, and scenes inspired entirely by your suggestions. Judges score the rounds\, decide the winners\, and shape the fun (as we boo them). No scripts. No safety nets. Just fast thinking\, bold choices\, and pure creative mayhem. \nThis isn’t your parents’ improv show\, unless your parents were super cool.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/seattle-theatresports-2026-test/2026-04-10/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Theatresports-Yellow-Small.jpg
END:VEVENT
