CREATED:20260407T174710Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260407T174710Z
UID:10011583-1775930400-1775934000@www.unexpectedproductions.org
SUMMARY:No Strings Attached: An Improvised Puppet Show for Grownups
DESCRIPTION:Seattle’s ORIGINAL improvised puppet show for grownups. An improvised fever dream with googly eyes and lots of laughter \n\n\n\n\nAt Unexpected Productions’ Market Theater\, puppets let their hair down (or strings loose) in No Strings Attached—a hilarious\, adults improv puppet show. After a long day entertaining the kids\, these puppets are ready to play—singing bawdy songs\, cracking jokes\, and getting up to all kinds of outrageous fun. And the best part? You call the shots with your suggestions! \nDon’t miss this one-of-a-kind comedy show at Pike Place Market. It’s puppets\, it’s improv\, and it’s guaranteed to make you laugh. \nTHIS SHOW CONTAINS MATURE CONTENT\, LANGUAGE\, AND SITUATIONS
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/no-strings-attached-an-improvised-puppet-show-for-grownups-4/2026-04-11/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/PPM-No-strings.jpg
END:VEVENT
