SUMMARY:Spellbound: An Improvised Romantasy
DESCRIPTION:Epic fantasy meets heart-pounding romance in a one-night-only improvised saga.\n\n\n\nSpellbound is a bold\, fun\, fully improvised romantasy where epic fantasy and big feelings take center stage. Inspired by books like A Court of Thorns and Roses and Fourth Wing\, our improvisers build a brand-new magical world on the spot using your ideas. \nExpect dramatic romance\, dangerous magic\, surprising twists\, and characters who fall hard\, mess up spectacularly\, and make very questionable choices in the name of love. It is playful\, passionate\, audience-powered storytelling with high stakes and zero scripts. Every show is a fresh fantasy adventure that only happens once.
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/spellbound-an-improvised-romantasy/2026-04-17/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike Place Market\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
END:VEVENT
